\textbf{2. Overall Description}


\textbf{2.1 Product Perspective}

The system is a standalone web application tailored for students. It interacts with external authentication providers (Google) for seamless login experiences. It assumes the existence of a backend administration panel managed separately.

\textbf{2.2 Product Functions}

The main functions of the user-facing system are:

