\end{minipage} \\
\midrule()
\endhead
FR-001 & Authentication & Registration, Standard Login, and Google OAuth Login. \\
FR-002 & Profile Management & Viewing and editing user information and avatar. \\
FR-003 & Exam Browsing \& Search & Finding exams, filtering, and viewing exam details. \\
FR-004 & Exam Execution & Taking exams, tracking time per part, saving snapshots, and automatic grading. \\
FR-005 & Results \& Leaderboard & Reviewing detailed answers and viewing competitive rankings. \\
FR-006 & Course \& Lesson Learning & Browsing courses and tracking lesson progress. \\
FR-007 & Document Browsing & Viewing and downloading study materials. \\
