\textbf{Basic Path} & \begin{minipage}[t]{\linewidth}\raggedright
\begin{quote}
1. System displays the overall score, time spent, and detailed breakdown per question.

2. User reviews explanations for incorrect answers.

3. User clicks "View Leaderboard".

4. System displays the top-ranking students for that specific exam based on score and time.
\end{quote}
\end{minipage} \\
\textbf{Postcondition} & User understands their performance metrics. \\
\textbf{Exception Paths} & Data retrieval error from the leaderboard service. \\
\textbf{Other} & Ranking is updated in real-time. \\
\bottomrule()
\end{longtable}

