\end{longtable}

\textbf{4. Non-Functional Requirements}

\textbf{4.1 Performance}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  Exam rendering must load swiftly. Pre-fetching question images/resources is recommended.
\item
  Snapshot syncing during exams must be asynchronous (AJAX) to prevent blocking the user interface.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{4.2 Security}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  Exam \texttt{session\_key} acts as an anti-tampering measure.
\item
  SQL injection prevention via ORM or prepared statements.
\item
  Authentication cookies must be HttpOnly and Secure.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{4.3 Usability}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  The exam interface must feature a fixed, visible countdown timer.
\item
  Clear visual indicators for answered vs. unanswered questions in the navigation palette.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{4.4 Maintainability}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  Strict MVC architecture (\texttt{Models}, \texttt{Views}, \texttt{Controllers}, \texttt{Services}).
\item
  Modular Blade components in \texttt{resources/views/user/components} to reuse UI elements across pages.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{5. External Interface Requirements}


\textbf{5.1 User Interface}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  \textbf{Home Page (\texttt{home.blade.php})}: Course recommendations, latest exams, statistics.
\item
  \textbf{Exam Detail (\texttt{exam-detail.blade.php})}: Description, rules, and entry point.
\item
  \textbf{Exam Interface (\texttt{exam.blade.php})}: Split view for Passage Groups (reading text on left, questions on right), question palette, timer.
\item
  \textbf{Profile (\texttt{profile.blade.php})}: User information, avatar upload, and history.
\item
  \textbf{Leaderboard (\texttt{leaderboard.blade.php})}: Tabular view of top scores for specific exams.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{5.2 Software Interfaces}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  \textbf{Google OAuth}: Communicates via HTTPS to retrieve user email, display\_name, and avatar.
\item
  \textbf{Database Engine}: MySQL interface for relational queries.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{5.3 Hardware Interfaces}

No special hardware is required. The system works on any device with a
modern web browser and internet access.

\textbf{5.4 Communication Interfaces}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  HTTPS --- all communication between the browser and the server must be
  encrypted.
\item
  REST API --- used to connect to the internal endpoints for exam syncing.
\end{itemize}

