\textbf{7. Project Scope, Constraints \& Limitations}

\textbf{7.1 What is included}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  Full user-facing exam lifecycle (Execution, Grading, Leaderboard).
\item
  Course and Document distribution.
\item
  Google Authentication integration.
\item
  Profile management interfaces.
\item
  Commenting and user interaction system.
\end{itemize}

\textbf{7.2 What is NOT included (Out of Scope)}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  Administrator Dashboard and AI Question Parsing (handled in a separate document).
\item
  Automated proctoring (webcam recording/eye tracking).
\item
  VIP/Pro subscription plans and payment gateway integration.
\item
  E-commerce features (Shopping, Orders, and Reward Withdrawals).
\item
  Web scraping or automated content crawling (DOM Crawler).
\end{itemize}

\textbf{7.3 Constraints}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  The system must process complex question formats natively (True/False clusters, short answers) requiring specialized DB tables.
\item
  The system must use HTTPS and follow basic OWASP security guidelines
  (see Section 4.2).
\end{itemize}

\textbf{7.4 Limitations}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  The system has not been load-tested for large numbers of concurrent
  users beyond those specified in Section 4.1.
\end{itemize}

